channel.name: Whakaata Maori NZ
channel.title: Homesteads
channel.desc: Kitemoana Street is an urban papak?inga situated in one of the most affluent areas in Auckland City. This episode tells the story of how these Ng?ti Wh?tua ki Orakei descendants came to reside on this street, highlighting significant events that impacted their iwi. (R).
